column10: Vehicle sped around multiple cars who had stopped to let pedestrians use crosswalks and nearly struck pedestrians.

This is not the only near miss I have experienced at this intersection- merely the most recent. Myself and another mother picked their child up from after school clubs at nearby Maury Elementary School and attempted to cross the street in the crosswalk.
